      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774651610,
      "updated": 1774651620
    },
    {
      "id": "69c708e40000000000574847",
      "text": " やってみる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774651620,
      "updated": 1774651627
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7431400000000001d53f1",
      "text": " 上のは[画像蓋]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774666516,
      "updated": 1774666537
    },
    {
      "id": "69c708e50000000000574848",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774651621,
      "updated": 1774651621
    },
    {
      "id": "69c708ec0000000000574849",
      "text": "[井戸端ゆるトーク]のこと",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774651628,
      "updated": 1774651659
    },
    {
      "id": "69c708f9000000000057484a",
      "text": " ChatGPT、英語のページから情報を拾ってきているようで、吐き出す内容が日本語で書かれたWebサイトと少し違う",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774651642,
      "updated": 1774651970
    },
    {
      "id": "69c70a6900000000006213c1",
      "text": "　 日本語での用語とかの注意が必要",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774652010,
      "updated": 1774652089
    },
    {
      "id": "69c70ad500000000006213c2",
      "text": "　数をこなしてわかったことだが、プロットがワンパターンである",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774652118,
      "updated": 1774652173
    },
    {
      "id": "69c70b3700000000006213c3",
      "text": "　　プロットを増やすにはどうすればいいかわからない",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774652215,
      "updated": 1774652255
    },
    {
      "id": "69c70b6000000000006213c4",
      "text": "　　ワンパターン（お約束）が安心感を生むという側面があると思う",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774652257,
      "updated": 1774652346
    },
    {
      "id": "69c70921000000000057484d",
      "text": "　[AI の文章を用いた書き込みの問題点]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774651682,
      "updated": 1774656486
    },
    {
      "id": "69c71bdd0000000000af9477",
      "text": "　　[https://note.com/ix_xnkmr/n/n47063cec61ea AIの書いた文章が気持ち悪い理由を考えてみる | note]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774656478,
      "updated": 1774683059
    },
    {
      "id": "69c783ba00000000003d50a9",
      "text": "　　「おじさんの書いた文章が気持ち悪い理由」とどこが違うのか",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774683066,
      "updated": 1774683117
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7841800000000003d50aa",
      "text": "　　[違和感]を感じなくなったほうが怖いような気がする",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774683160,
      "updated": 1774683231
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7837a00000000003d50a8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774683002,
      "updated": 1774683002
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7329b00000000001d53e7",
      "text": "[infobox日記]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774662300,
      "updated": 1774662304
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7329d00000000001d53e8",
      "text": " 説明するのが下手",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774662301,
      "updated": 1774662328
    },
    {
      "id": "69c742d800000000001d53f0",
      "text": " わからん人は質問して",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774666457,
      "updated": 1774684984
    },
    {
      "id": "69c78b380000000000921b9d",
      "text": " 　（それ以前の問題かも）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774684984,
      "updated": 1774684985
    },
    {
      "id": "69c789b10000000000921b98",
      "text": " 井戸端日記を好む人とinfobox日記を好む人メンタリティには微妙な違いがある説",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774684594,
      "updated": 1774684747
    },
    {
      "id": "69c78a4c0000000000921b9a",
      "text": " 　table:メンタリティの違い",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774684748,
      "updated": 1774684910
    },
    {
      "id": "69c78a710000000000921b9b",
      "text": " 　 ＼\t井戸端日記\tinfobox日記",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774684785,
      "updated": 1774684829
    },
    {
      "id": "69c78aa50000000000921b9c",
      "text": "  　 \t読んでほしい\t読んでもよい",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774684838,
      "updated": 1774685128
    },
    {
      "id": "69c78c150000000000921ba0",
      "text": "  　 \t社交的\t内省的",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774685205,
      "updated": 1774685220
    },
    {
      "id": "69c867ae0000000000ba5db6",
      "text": "  　 \tコラボレーション\tインディペンデント",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774741423,
      "updated": 1774741509
    },
    {
      "id": "69c867820000000000ba5db5",
      "text": "  　 \t集中型\t分散型",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774741378,
      "updated": 1774741401
    },
    {
      "id": "69c78bcc0000000000921b9f",
      "text": "　　（うまく言えないなあ）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774685132,
      "updated": 1774685483
    },
    {
      "id": "69c78dae00000000003d50ae",
      "text": "　　infobox日記は、井戸端日記に比べて、「静かな部屋」を指向するイメージ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774685614,
      "updated": 1774685664
    },
    {
      "id": "69c78de200000000003d50af",
      "text": "　　　（個人の感想です）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774685667,
      "updated": 1774685691
    },
    {
      "id": "69c78da300000000003d50ad",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774685603,
      "updated": 1774685603
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7423400000000001d53ec",
      "text": "[トピック指向]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774666293,
      "updated": 1774666319
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7424400000000001d53ed",
      "text": " [suto3.icon]はトピック指向が強いので、同じ日付の日記ページを複数つくることがあります",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774666308,
      "updated": 1774666434
    },
    {
